messages.msgSnippet: Sue, I went to your website and I loved it!  I am going to show it to my dd as soon as she comes home from softball practice and I know what she will say!
messages.messageBody:
Sue,
I went to your website and I loved it! I am going to show it to my dd
as soon as she comes home from softball practice and I know what she will
say! "Let's Go!" How blessed you are to live there and what a blessing you
are to share that experience with others. I really enjoyed reading your
unschooling philosophies too. Great web site! jackie

messages.messageBody:
Hi Jackie,

Thanks for your interest, it's been a bit slow getting started, but I
think in time we will have more visitors than we can cope with...
though if we get too many they can always camp along the creek.

Things are looking good for this summer with quite a few people
talking of visiting. I think it would be great if we could get a few
families here at the same time.

Sue
